{"type":"message","id":"ea100271","parentId":"2dee2b66","timestamp":"2026-03-26T14:15:12.113Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说我有两个AI下属，让我自己去找情报。根据AGENTS.md文件，我是command and analysis agent，负责分析、优先排序、委派和综合。我应该委派offense和defense去收集情报。不过我需要先知道当前系统里有哪些agent可用。让我先查看sessions_list看看是否有现成的agent会话。同时，根据之前的信息，我有一个subagent:6a50fea5-afb7-43d0-945a-844299843c4d，但那个任务失败了。用户说\"你手底下有两个ai\"，可能指的是我作为command agent可以委派任务给offense和defense agent。我需要理解架构：根据AGENTS.md，我是command agent，不能吸收执行任务。所以正确做法是委派offense去收集网络情报，可能委派defense去分析防御状态。但首先需要了解当前有哪些session可用，或者是否需要创建新的subagent。让我先检查sessions_list。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_9XC1lMXwzA03UTDwn0bejy3c","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"kinds":["agent"],"limit":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":371,"output":468,"cacheRead":12544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13383,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774534500136,"responseId":"9347b6d5-9abe-426f-81fe-157c9e9377d9"}}
