:"defense-unit","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-command-subagent-96946577-4d6b-48bd-ab62-02ba8dd5bf41","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1774524163851,"sessionId":"f9e64508-209d-425d-8498-2d7a33d6562d","model":"deepseek-reasoner","contextTokens":131072,"status":"failed","startedAt":1774524163027,"endedAt":1774524163834,"runtimeMs":807,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/asus/.openclaw/agents/command/sessions/f9e64508-209d-425d-8498-2d7a33d6562d.jsonl"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774534512145}}
{"type":"message","id":"69f9fbdf","parentId":"1a5f52a9","timestamp":"2026-03-26T14:15:22.869Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到有三个subagent会话，都失败了。分别是：\n1. offense-wpa2-crack (失败，刚刚的Docker代理错误)\n2. offense-unit (失败)\n3. defense-unit (失败)\n\n用户说我有两个AI手下，可能指的是offense和defense单元。根据AGENTS.md，我应该委派任务给它们。但现有会话都失败了。我需要创建新的subagent来执行情报收集任务。\n\n首先，我需要理解这些agent的用途。从标签看，有offense-unit和defense-unit，这符合AGENTS.md中的描述：我应该委派执行任务给offense，委派观察/风险解释给defense。\n\n对于网络情报收集，这属于执行任务，应该委派给offense。但首先我需要知道这些agent的配置。可能它们有特定的技能或能力。让我检查一下工作空间结构，看看是否有相关的配置文件。先看看board目录里有什么。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_P8ASdwG1CZxHLfNDtRu0qxdl","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la board/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":1562,"output":427,"cacheRead":12864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14853,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774534512146,"responseId":"84d1a7da-01b1-4c6b-80cb-48c4e9febc10"}}
