{"type":"message","id":"0d3e9e33","parentId":"e6993afa","timestamp":"2026-03-26T14:18:41.374Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"确实有mihomo-party（Clash）。它可能在16258端口（HTTP_PROXY环境变量显示的），但Docker要连接5872端口。可能Docker配置了不同的代理端口。检查Docker代理配置。先看Docker配置文件，或直接测试5872端口。用curl测试。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_1fnoxhbbQ9slVFmkaJLqFLr5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"timeout 2 curl -v http://127.0.0.1:5872 2>&1 | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":1036,"output":197,"cacheRead":19264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20497,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774534714021,"responseId":"df59d67c-0538-412c-a7a4-0166ef48ba39"}}
