{"type":"message","id":"e40ac4b8","parentId":"c3be4c16","timestamp":"2026-03-26T14:18:51.316Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"5872端口没开。Docker配置可能指向错误的代理端口。需要检查Docker的代理配置。通常Docker通过环境变量或daemon.json配置代理。看看docker info或配置文件。先检查是否有docker.service的代理设置。但用户说Clash受保护不能修改，可能需要调整Docker配置指向正确的代理端口（16258）。或者直接绕过Docker使用系统工具。\n\n先检查当前代理环境变量，Docker可能使用这些变量。环境变量显示HTTP_PROXY=http://127.0.0.1:16258，但Docker错误显示连接127.0.0.1:5872，说明Docker没使用这些变量。可能是Docker daemon配置的代理。\n\n检查docker daemon配置。看看/etc/docker/daemon.json。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_8NMoP6VOsyjxbcX0xvqDy9JY","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /etc/docker/daemon.json 2>/dev/null || echo \"文件不存在\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":355,"output":392,"cacheRead":20288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21035,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774534721397,"responseId":"5fb2c0ff-6398-4bf6-bd8f-c712866509c4"}}
