{"type":"message","id":"ac957094","parentId":"0ff505b9","timestamp":"2026-03-26T14:47:48.398Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户已授权执行深度无线侦察。现在需要调用合适的工具来扫描目标AP的详细信息。\n\n首先检查有哪些工具可用。之前看到aircrack-ng已安装，应包含airodump-ng。需要确认。同时需要获取root权限，可以使用sudo执行命令。\n\n计划步骤：\n1. 检查airodump-ng是否存在。\n2. 使用airodump-ng扫描目标AP（BSSID: D8:F6:07:DA:C0:E4，频道161）收集详细信标信息。\n3. 同时可能需要获取AP的IP地址以扫描UDP 8211端口。但AP的IP可能不在当前子网，或者需要通过其他方式获取。可以先扫描ARP缓存或尝试发现。\n\n考虑到之前网卡被屏蔽的问题，需要确认wlan1是否真的可用于监控模式。之前看到wlan1状态为\"PROMISC\"，可能已处于监控模式。\n\n开始执行。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_hT79c7cGUH9kCDApBTwa7duF","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which airodump-ng"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":59,"output":436,"cacheRead":31744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32239,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774536453525,"responseId":"a1882fc8-d5d7-4d91-8816-8b32f1705cf4"}}
