{"type":"message","id":"1ba0ce6b","parentId":"3891ea16","timestamp":"2026-03-26T14:48:10.888Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"airodump-ng在/usr/sbin/下。需要sudo权限运行。现在开始扫描目标AP。使用sudo执行airodump-ng，指定wlan1接口、BSSID和频道161，只扫描特定AP。同时可能需要输出到文件以便分析。\n\n但需要注意：airodump-ng可能会持续运行，需要控制时间。可以使用timeout命令限制扫描时间，比如30秒。同时为了避免干扰当前网络连接，使用wlan1接口。\n\n执行命令：sudo timeout 30 /usr/sbin/airodump-ng -c 161 --bssid D8:F6:07:DA:C0:E4 -w /tmp/ap_scan wlan1\n\n-w参数会生成带前缀的文件。然后可以读取输出文件。但airodump-ng输出到屏幕，也会写入文件。我们可以捕获标准输出和错误。使用sudo可能需要输入密码，但可能已经配置了免密sudo。先尝试。另外，需要先确保wlan1接口在监控模式。之前看到wlan1状态是\"PROMISC\"，但不确定是否监控模式。可以用iwconfig检查，但之前iwconfig命令没有。可以用ip link show wlan1查看标志。\n\n先检查wlan1接口状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_1HYkzD57vardiaPAI8QFDSn7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sudo ip link show wlan1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":249,"output":573,"cacheRead":32064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32886,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774536477380,"responseId":"7c648eae-0429-4677-ba27-8b7c5c3366a6"}}
