{"type":"message","id":"825b455a","parentId":"b65863b8","timestamp":"2026-03-26T15:43:30.936Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"需要sudo密码。wash需要root权限。不过我们已经有无密码sudo权限用于air*命令，但wash可能不在允许列表中。检查sudo -l输出显示只有air*和tcpdump可以无密码运行。wash可能需要密码。不过我们可以用airodump-ng监控WPS信号。但更简单的方法是：直接假设目标可能支持WPS，然后尝试reaver攻击。但reaver也需要sudo。或者我们可以创建一个有针对性的密码字典。\n\n先创建一个针对性密码字典文件。基于\"双不限\"的拼音变体、数字组合等。创建/tmp/targeted.txt。然后使用aircrack-ng的另一个实例进行破解，但使用不同的字典。不过aircrack-ng一次只能运行一个实例针对同一个cap文件吗？可能可以，但需要小心。或者我们可以用aircrack-ng的批处理模式。\n\n先创建针对性字典。想法：\"shuangbuxian\", \"shuangbuxian123\", \"sbx\", \"doubleunlimited\", \"doubleunlimited123\", \"双不限\", \"双不限2.4G\", \"12345678\", \"88888888\", \"11111111\", \"00000000\"等等。还有常见的简单密码。让我创建一个文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_UUHX7b0vyLhywpdDqrWhaHIv","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/tmp/targeted.txt","content":"shuangbuxian\nshuangbuxian123\nshuangbuxian888\nsbx\nsbx123\nsbx888\ndoubleunlimited\ndoubleunlimited123\nunlimited\nunlimited123\n双不限\n双不限2.4G\n双不限2.4\n12345678\n123456789\n88888888\n11111111\n00000000\n11223344\n123123123\npassword\nadmin\n1234\n12345\n123456\n1234567\n12345678\n123456789\n987654321\nqwerty\nqwertyuiop\nasdfghjkl\nzxcvbnm\niloveyou\nadmin123\nadmin888\npassword123\nwifi\nwifi123\nwifi888\nnetgear\nlinksys\ndlink\ntp-link\ntplink\nhuawei\nxiaomi\nmi\nchina\nchinese\nchina123\ncn\ncn123\n2024\n2025\n2026\n2023\n2022\n2021\n2020\n2019\n2018\n2017"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":199,"output":811,"cacheRead":74176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75186,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774539789494,"responseId":"cf00e5c2-5fad-4e89-b548-a517d11ca0df"}}
